Class Summary 
Class Description
Controller
This class is the controller for all the actions for the GUI and will connect with the TuitionManager to keep track of the Students.
Instate
This is the In-State Student class that extends Student.
International
This is the International Student class that extends Student.
Main
This is the class that can be used to build and run the GUI for the user.
Outstate
This is the Out-Of-State Student class that extends Student.
Proj3Terminal
This is the class used to run the terminal version of the Student Tuition Lister.
Student
This class is the abstract parent class for the different types of Students.
StudentList
This class makes a list of Students.
TuitionManager
This class is called when running the program.
